title: Fix the side effects on the recycler view.
message:
Fix the side effects on the recycler view.
The side effects were caused by recycled views still having their onButtonChangedListeners enabled.
When the checkboxes were reset when being recycled, those listeners would fire, undoing any action they did.
By setting the listeners to null before recycling the view, this is avoided.
